<p>For those who haven&#39;t already snorted their way out of reading the rest of this post, these are all famous songs involving some sort of fire, thus making them a &quot;torch song.&quot;</p>

<p>Putting aside my deficiencies, I imagine this could be a perfect Monday puzzle for pop music fans. Nice and consistent, each song title relating to fire somehow. And each of the songs Matt chose seem famous enough to be crossworthy.</p>

<p>I would have pegged it for a Wednesday puzzle, though, especially given a couple aspects of the fill:</p>

